- Mastering and dynamics: The description calls out tasteful compression that reveals microdetail, warm analogue tonality, and preserved dynamics and headroom. Those are exactly the mastering characteristics I prize (transparent, modern yet preserving headroom and dynamic nuance), and they avoid the heavy compression and punch‑forward approach I dislike.
