- Direct match to core tonal preferences: candidate 2 explicitly offers warm analogue texture and tape‑warm intimacy, which directly satisfies my stated desire for warm tape midrange and low‑compression analogue tone. That analogue warmth is a primary reason I prize AOR/pop material.
